name: Solchat
reason: A decentralized communication protocol allowing wallet-to-wallet text, voice, and video calls. Strong utility narrative with moderate insider holdings for development.

name: Synesis One
reason: Crowdsourcing platform for training AI datasets. Users earn rewards for providing data. Experimental economic model bridging gaming and AI infrastructure.

name: UpRock
reason: Mobile-first DePIN project utilizing spare internet bandwidth for AI data scraping. Strong growth metrics but relies heavily on the team's central coordination of data buyers.

name: Goatseus Maximus
reason: The first major token endorsed and promoted by an autonomous AI agent (Terminal of Truths). Represents a novel intersection of Memetics and AI behavior.

name: ai16z
reason: An AI-managed venture DAO. Investors trust an AI agent to make trading decisions. High innovation risk and reliance on the model's performance.

name: Act I: The AI Prophecy
reason: A multi-agent AI interaction experiment. Value is derived from the emerging narrative of the AI swarm. Highly speculative and community-driven.

name: FluxBot
reason: Telegram trading bot on Solana offering copy trading and sniping. High insider score due to the team's control over the bot infrastructure and fee collection.

name: Analysoor
reason: Pioneered a unique distribution method using block hash lotteries to prevent sniper bots. Highly experimental protocol with a niche but dedicated following.

name: Koii Network
reason: Distributed cloud computing platform rewarding users for running nodes. Bridges to Solana. Moderate centralization in the early stages of network bootstrapping.

name: Zerebro
reason: An AI agent that generates its own content and memes across social platforms. Represents the 'autonomous influencer' sector of the AI crypto market.
